{"word":"G3922 - παρεισέρχομαι - pareisérchomai - par-ice-er'-khom-ahee - Come in privily","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρεισέρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pareisérchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ice-er'-khom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come in privily</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வா, கள்ளத்தனமாய் நுழை"},{"paragraph":"1. to come in secretly or by stealth"},{"paragraph":"2. to enter in addition, come in besides"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1525 - εἰσέρχομαι - eisérchomai - ice-er'-khom-ahee/1525\">G1525</a>; to <i>come in along side</i>, that is, <i>supervene additionally</i> or <i>stealthily:</i> - come in privily, enter.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1330/1330\">G1330</a>, <a href=\"#/G1525/1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831/1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904/1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064/2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3922/3922\">G3922</a>, <a href=\"#/G3928/3928\">G3928</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022/4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281/4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4334/4334\">G4334</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905/4905\">G4905</a>, <a href=\"#/G565/565\">G565</a>"}]}